						               													<description>Pikemen is a game that uses Icehouse Pieces and a standard 8&amp;times;8 board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Pieces are warriors with long spears known as &amp;quot;Pikes.&amp;quot; Each turn a Pikeman may charge in the direction he is pointing (move any number of spaces in a straight line) and then reorient his pike in a different direction, including straight up for defense. When in defense, a piece can only be captured by a larger piece.  When pointing, a piece may be captured by any other piece.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Captured pieces are worth different points depending on their size: 1 for small, 2 for medium, 3 for large.  The player who captures a number of enemy Pikemen worth a given amount first wins-- usually 12 points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Online Play&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Super Duper Games&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Re-implemented by Star Fleet Scramble&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
